{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/java/start_gradle_project/lombok/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"4fbf5cfc-891d-5eca-b711-5765d1505e22","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>Gradle Proejct 에 Lombok 을 추가하는 가장 정석적이고 깔끔한 방법을 소개하고자 합니다. 추가적으로 Intellij IDE 에서 해야되는 간단한 설정도 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">종류</th>\n<th>환경</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OS</td>\n<td>M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IDE</td>\n<td>Intellij(2022.1.2)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Java</td>\n<td>jdk17 (temurin)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"gradle-project-에-lombok-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gradle project 에 lombok 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Project 에 Lombok 적용하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>주로 라이브러리에 추가하는 통상적인 방법과 달리 Gralde Project는 라이브러리를 추가하지 않아도 plugin 으로 간단히 Lombok을 적용할 수 있습니다.\n<a href=\"https://plugins.gradle.org/plugin/io.freefair.lombok\">lombok plugins guide</a> 에 접속하여 버전과 적용 방법을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"bulidgradle-에-lombok-plugin-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bulidgradle-%EC%97%90-lombok-plugin-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"bulidgradle 에 lombok plugin 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bulid.gradle 에 lombok plugin 추가</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    plugins <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id \"io.freefair.lombok\" version \"6.5.0.2\"\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Dependences 에 의존성과 annotation 설정을 해야하는 일반 gradle 환경과 달리 간단하게 적용할 수 있는 것이 가장 큰 장점입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"intellij-에-lombok-설정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"intellij 에 lombok 설정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ 에 Lombok 설정하기</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"플러그인-목록에-lombok-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"플러그인 목록에 lombok 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>플러그인 목록에 Lombok 추가</h3>\n<p>최신 Intellij 는 기본 플러그인에 Lombok 이 포함되어 있으며 플러그인 활성화가 되어있습니다. 따라서 정상적으로 활성화 되어있는지 확인만 하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">Setting > Plugins</code> 를 차례로 클릭한 뒤 상단의 <code class=\"language-text\">Installed</code> 탭을 클릭합니다. 그 후 검색창에 <strong>Lombok</strong> 이 깔려있는지, 체크박스가 체크되어있는지 확인하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lombok plugin download\"\n        title=\"lombok plugin download\"\n        src=\"/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/37523/lombok-download_plugin.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/e9ff0/lombok-download_plugin.png 180w,\n/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/f21e7/lombok-download_plugin.png 360w,\n/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/37523/lombok-download_plugin.png 720w,\n/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/302a4/lombok-download_plugin.png 1080w,\n/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/07a9c/lombok-download_plugin.png 1440w,\n/static/bf14a41e810a1606907b389c179c5ac2/94cea/lombok-download_plugin.png 1940w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"intellij-설정-중-annotaion-processing-을-활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91-annotaion-processing-%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"intellij 설정 중 annotaion processing 을 활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IntelliJ 설정 중 Annotaion Processing 을 활성화</h3>\n<p>마지막으로 Annotation Processing 이 활성화 되어있는지 확인합니다.</p>\n<p>먼저 <code class=\"language-text\">Setting > Build, Execution, Deployment > Compiler > Annotation Processors</code> 를 차례로 클릭한 뒤 <code class=\"language-text\">Enable annotation processing</code> 이 체크 되어있는지 확인하면 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.77777777777777%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"annotation processing enable\"\n        title=\"annotation processing enable\"\n        src=\"/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/37523/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/e9ff0/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 180w,\n/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/f21e7/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 360w,\n/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/37523/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 720w,\n/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/302a4/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 1080w,\n/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/07a9c/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 1440w,\n/static/7df2f98efa78861a82ed75cc9b89e23c/a9577/lombok-enable_annotation_processing.png 1784w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"적용-테스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"적용 테스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용 테스트</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>위 내용을 그대로 따랐을 경우 설정이 모두 끝났습니다. lombok annotation 을 사용하여 제대로 적용하였는지 확인합니다.\n예제에서는 @Sl4j annotation 을 사용하여 제대로 설정하였는지 테스트 하도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">lombok<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>extern<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>slf4j<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Slf4j</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Slf4j</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">LombokAnnotationTest</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> args<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        log<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"lombok 의 {} annotation 을 사용하여 적용되었는지 테스트합니다. \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@Sl4j\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAdklEQVQI1z2NSw6AIBBDPZKflQJ+QEXQRPGvifH+p6hhFi5e0mk7aVB2OzLlwJuZSOUEVjuIdiV8XnQ76Vxv4M1CfdEuSNWE0hzI9Uq+z4N6uOnBI/vr13p8IO0J415U9oDsT6jhotEw04iZQcQMEmERc0u35wMYdEkb5K3s8QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"test result\"\n        title=\"test result\"\n        src=\"/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/37523/lombok-result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/e9ff0/lombok-result.png 180w,\n/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/f21e7/lombok-result.png 360w,\n/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/37523/lombok-result.png 720w,\n/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/302a4/lombok-result.png 1080w,\n/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/07a9c/lombok-result.png 1440w,\n/static/52b6b9ef4314d70adde8cdfd7f13c817/cea38/lombok-result.png 1644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>이상으로 Gradle Project 에 Lombok 을 간단히 적용하는 방법에 대해서 알아보았습니다. 감사합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\">개요</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Gradle Project 에 Lombok 적용하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#bulidgradle-%EC%97%90-lombok-plugin-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">bulid.gradle 에 lombok plugin 추가</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">IntelliJ 에 Lombok 설정하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D%EC%97%90-lombok-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">플러그인 목록에 Lombok 추가</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#intellij-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%A4%91-annotaion-processing-%EC%9D%84-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\">IntelliJ 설정 중 Annotaion Processing 을 활성화</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\">적용 테스트</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"개요 Gradle Proejct 에 Lombok 을 추가하는 가장 정석적이고 깔끔한 방법을 소개하고자 합니다. 추가적으로 Intellij IDE 에서 해야되는 간단한 설정도 확인할 수 있습니다. 종류 환경 OS M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4) IDE Intellij(2022.1.2) Java jdk17 (temurin) Gradle Project 에 Lombok 적용하기 주로 라이브러리에 추가하는 통상적인 방법과 달리 Gralde Project는 라이브러리를 추가하지 않아도 plugin 으로 간단히 Lombok을 적용할 수 있습니다.\nlombok plugins guide 에 접속하여 버전과 적용 방법을 확인할 수 있습니다. bulid.gradle 에 lombok plugin 추가 Dependences 에 의존성과 annotation 설정을 해야하는 일반 gradle 환경과 달리 간단하게 적용할 수 있는 것이 가장 큰 장점입니다. IntelliJ 에 Lombok 설정하기 플러…","frontmatter":{"date":"June 20, 2022","title":"[Java] Gradle Project lombok 설정","categories":"java spring","author":"olkkani","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/java/start_gradle_project/lombok/"}},"next":{"id":"d53b921b-ef2e-59e0-aab3-f49261a948f7","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>java 에서 절대 경로의 파일을 가져오려고 하는 경우, 각 OS별로 파일 구분자를 다르게 지정해야합니다. 기존에 OS 별 구분자를 지정하지 않았거나 하드 코딩 하였다면 Paths 라이브러리를 사용하여 개선해보도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"경로-구분자를-삽입하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%BD%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B5%AC%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"경로 구분자를 삽입하는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>경로 구분자를 삽입하는 방법</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"하드-코딩으로-절대경로-지정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%98%EB%93%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%94%A9%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%88%EB%8C%80%EA%B2%BD%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A7%80%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"하드 코딩으로 절대경로 지정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>하드 코딩으로 절대경로 지정하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:/sampleFile/testimage.png\"</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// console</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">D</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sampleFile<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>testImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>png</code></pre></div>\n<p>가장 간결한 방법이지만 운영체제마다 구분자가 조금씩 다르게 때문에 여러 환경을 고려한다면 권장하지 않습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"fileseparator-로-파일-구분자-삽입하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fileseparator-%EB%A1%9C-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"fileseparator 로 파일 구분자 삽입하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>File.separator 로 파일 구분자 삽입하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">\n<span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"D:\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>separator <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"sampleFile\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> \n\t<span class=\"token class-name\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>separator <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"testImage.jpg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// console</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">D</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sampleFile<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>testImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>png</code></pre></div>\n<p>직접 실행한다면 각 운영체제에 맞춰 파일 구분자가 다르게 삽입되는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다. 다만  하드코딩보다 훨씬 코드가 길고 가독성이 떨어져서 해당 방법으로 구분자를 삽입하고 있다면 다음 방법으로 수정하는 것이 좋습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"pathget-으로-파일-구분자-삽입하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pathget-%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"pathget 으로 파일 구분자 삽입하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Path.get() 으로 파일 구분자 삽입하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Paths</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"D:\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">\"sampleFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"testImage.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">System</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>out<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">println</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token comment\">// console</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">D</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sampleFile<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>testImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>png</code></pre></div>\n<p>File.separator 랑 결과는 같지만 코드가 더 짧고 가독성이 좋습니다.\n성능상 차이가 크지 않다면 여러모로 Path.get() 을 사용하는 것이 좋아보입니다.</p>\n<p>지금까지 File.separator 을 대체할 수 있는 Path.get()에 대해서 간단하게 소개해봤습니다.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 30, 2022","title":"[Java] 파일 구분자 File.separator 대신 Path 사용하기","categories":"java","author":"olkkani","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/java/path/"}},"prev":{"id":"bef1f628-90be-5e9a-80e7-d725eb1734eb","html":"<h2 id=\"개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"개요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개요</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>Gradle Project 에 Junit5 + AssertThat 을 설정해보도록 하겠습니다.</p>\n<p>맥락을 이해한다면 Spring 프레임워크를 사용하거나 Maven Project 에도 적용할 수 있으니 참고 바랍니다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">종류</th>\n<th>환경</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">OS</td>\n<td>M1 Mac(Monterey 12.4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">IDE</td>\n<td>Intellij(2022.1.2)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">Java</td>\n<td>jdk17 (temurin)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"gradle-project-에-junit5-라이브러리-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-junit5-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"gradle project 에 junit5 라이브러리 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Project 에 JUnit5 라이브러리 추가</h2>\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/java_testing.html#using_junit5\">Gradle Junit5 Use Guide</a>\n를 확인하여 손쉽게 JUnit5 를 적용할 수 있습니다. 직접적인 관련은 없지만 assertThat 을 사용하기 위해서 <strong>assertj</strong> 종속성도 같이 추가했습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"gradle-project-buildgradle-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-project-buildgradle-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"gradle project buildgradle 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Project build.gradle 수정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 의존성 추가</span>\ndependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  testImplementation 'org.junit.jupiter<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>junit<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>jupiter<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>5.8.2'\n  testImplementation 'org.assertj<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>assertj<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>core<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>3.23.1'\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">...</span>(생략)\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Junit5 활성화</span>\ntest <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  useJUnitPlatform()\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"gradle-spring-환경에서-junit5-라이브러리-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gradle-spring-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-junit5-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"gradle spring 환경에서 junit5 라이브러리 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gradle Spring 환경에서 junit5 라이브러리 추가</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>Gradle 과 동일하게 설정해도 무관하지만 Spring boot 에는 <strong>spring-boot-starter-test</strong> 가 존재하기 때문에 종속성을 다르게 가져갈 필요가 있습니다.\n하위 의존성을 잘 살펴보면 jupiter 를 비롯한 여러 라이브러리를 포함하는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"srping-project-buildgradle-파일-수정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#srping-project-buildgradle-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"srping project buildgradle 파일 수정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Srping Project build.gradle 파일 수정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">    <span class=\"token comment\"># 의존성 추가</span>\n    dependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        testImplementation 'org.springframework.boot<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>spring<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>boot<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>starter<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>test<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>2.7.0'\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">...</span>(생략)\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># Junit5 활성화</span>\n    test <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      useJUnitPlatform()\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"homcrest-종속성-제외\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#homcrest-%EC%A2%85%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8\" aria-label=\"homcrest 종속성 제외 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>homcrest 종속성 제외</h3>\n<p>spring-boot-stater-test 에는 <strong>hamcrest</strong> 와 <strong>assertj</strong> 가 기본적으로 포함되어 있기때문에 추가하는 수고를 덜합니다.</p>\n<p>다만 homcrest 대신 assertj 를 사용할 예정이므로 hamcrest 는 종속성에서 제외하도록 하겠습니다. 필수는 아니므로 본인 선택에 따라 제외하도록 합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">configurations <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  all<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">exclude module</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'org.hamcrest'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"assert-that-static-import-사용법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#assert-that-static-import-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"assert that static import 사용법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Assert That Static Import 사용법</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>AssertThat 을 알고 있다면 assertThat 을 Static Import 하여 사용하는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>assertThat() 을 사용하기 위해서는 매번 타이핑하여 Static Import 해야합니다만, IDE 에 따라서 그 수고를 덜어줄 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"13-intellij-에서-static-import-하는--일반적인-방법-안될-가능성-높음\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#13-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94--%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EC%95%88%EB%90%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5%EC%84%B1-%EB%86%92%EC%9D%8C\" aria-label=\"13 intellij 에서 static import 하는  일반적인 방법 안될 가능성 높음 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(1/3) IntelliJ 에서 Static Import 하는  일반적인 방법 (안될 가능성 높음)</h3>\n<p>IntelliJ 를 사용하시는 많은 분들은 <code class=\"language-text\">assertThat()</code> 까지 입력한 후 <strong>Show Context Action</strong> (Mac: ⌥⏎ Windows: alt+enter) 로 static import 하여 사용합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 519px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"not found static import method\"\n        title=\"not found static import method\"\n        src=\"/static/e3033dca00a9f40e69c40159860016d3/b23ad/JUnit5-assertThat_not_found_static_import.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e3033dca00a9f40e69c40159860016d3/e9ff0/JUnit5-assertThat_not_found_static_import.png 180w,\n/static/e3033dca00a9f40e69c40159860016d3/f21e7/JUnit5-assertThat_not_found_static_import.png 360w,\n/static/e3033dca00a9f40e69c40159860016d3/b23ad/JUnit5-assertThat_not_found_static_import.png 519w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 519px) 100vw, 519px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n다만 저는 static import method 라는 선택지가 나오지 않아서 난처했습니다. 인터넷에 검색했을 땐 모두 해당 방법이 나오므로 시도해본 뒤 저랑 같은 상황이면 빠르게 다음 방법으로 넘어가도록 합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"23-intellij-에서-static-import-하는-공식-가이드-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#23-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B3%B5%EC%8B%9D-%EA%B0%80%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"23 intellij 에서 static import 하는 공식 가이드 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(2/3) Intellij 에서 Static Import 하는 공식 가이드 방법</h3>\n<p>조금 찾아보니 IntelliJ 공식 가이드가 존재합니다.\n<a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/guide/tips/assert-that/\">Intellij Assert That Import Guide</a> 에서 영상을 확인할 수 있으므로 글 보다는 영상을 직접 확인하는 것이 이해가 빠릅니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Assertions.assertThat()</code> 을 입력하여 assertj 를 Import 한다.</li>\n<li>Assertions 부분을 지운다.</li>\n<li>.asserThat() 에서 커서를 .와 a 사이로 옮긴 후 <strong>⌥⏎</strong> (Windows: alt+enter) 를 누른 뒤 <strong>import static method</strong> 를 선택합니다.</li>\n<li>import 항목 중 <code class=\"language-text\">Assertions.assertThat</code> 을 선택합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>확실히 유효한 방법이나 조금 불편합니다. 저는 불편해서 세 번째 방법을 주로 사용합니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"33-intellij-에서-static-import-하는-최종-방법-개인적으로-쓰는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#33-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A2%85-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%B8%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%93%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"33 intellij 에서 static import 하는 최종 방법 개인적으로 쓰는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>(3/3) IntelliJ 에서 Static import 하는 최종 방법 (개인적으로 쓰는 방법)</h3>\n<p>조금 사용하다보니깐 처음 방법과 다르지 않은 방법을 발견하여 현재 이 방법으로 사용하는 중입니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">assertThat()</code> 을 입력한다.</li>\n<li>커서 포인트르 a 왼쪽으로 이동한다.</li>\n<li><strong>⌥⏎</strong> 를 눌러 <strong>import static method</strong> 를 선택한다.</li>\n<li>import 항목 중 <code class=\"language-text\">Assertions.assertThat</code> 을 선택합니다.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>IntelliJ 에서 import static method 하는 방법은 검색해도 잘 나오지 않아 곤란했는데 저와 비슷한 분들에게 도움이 되었으면하는 바람입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"junit5-적용-test\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#junit5-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-test\" aria-label=\"junit5 적용 test permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JUnit5 적용 Test</h2>\n<hr>\n<p>모든 설정이 완료되었다면 정상적으로 적용되었는지 테스트합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token import static\"><span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>assertj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>core<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>api<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Assertions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token static\">assertThat</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token import\"><span class=\"token namespace\">org<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>junit<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>jupiter<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>api<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></span><span class=\"token class-name\">Test</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Junit5_를_프로젝트에_정상적으로_적용하였는지_테스트</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">JUnit5Test</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Test</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> 숫자비교<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">Long</span> id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1L</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">assertThat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isEqualTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Test</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> 문자비교<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"chanjin_ahn\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">assertThat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">isEqualTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"chanjin_ahn\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"JUnit5 Test\"\n        title=\"JUnit5 Test\"\n        src=\"/static/2bb94d22214bf4e0e805a3b8ed0e7698/37523/JUnit5-test.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2bb94d22214bf4e0e805a3b8ed0e7698/e9ff0/JUnit5-test.png 180w,\n/static/2bb94d22214bf4e0e805a3b8ed0e7698/f21e7/JUnit5-test.png 360w,\n/static/2bb94d22214bf4e0e805a3b8ed0e7698/37523/JUnit5-test.png 720w,\n/static/2bb94d22214bf4e0e805a3b8ed0e7698/35a31/JUnit5-test.png 1028w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>실행시 위와 같다면 정상입니다. 이번 포스팅은 여기까지입니다. 부족한 점이 많으니 틀린 부분이 있다면 지적 부탁드립니다. 감사합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\">개요</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gradle-project-%EC%97%90-junit5-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">Gradle Project 에 JUnit5 라이브러리 추가</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#gradle-project-buildgradle-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\">Gradle Project build.gradle 수정</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#gradle-spring-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-junit5-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">Gradle Spring 환경에서 junit5 라이브러리 추가</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#srping-project-buildgradle-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\">Srping Project build.gradle 파일 수정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#homcrest-%EC%A2%85%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8\">homcrest 종속성 제외</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#assert-that-static-import-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%B2%95\">Assert That Static Import 사용법</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#13-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94--%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EC%95%88%EB%90%A0-%EA%B0%80%EB%8A%A5%EC%84%B1-%EB%86%92%EC%9D%8C\">(1/3) IntelliJ 에서 Static Import 하는  일반적인 방법 (안될 가능성 높음)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#23-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B3%B5%EC%8B%9D-%EA%B0%80%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">(2/3) Intellij 에서 Static Import 하는 공식 가이드 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#33-intellij-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-static-import-%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A2%85-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9D%B8%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%93%B0%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">(3/3) IntelliJ 에서 Static import 하는 최종 방법 (개인적으로 쓰는 방법)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#junit5-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9-test\">JUnit5 적용 Test</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"June 21, 2022","title":"[Gradle] Gradle Project 에 JUnit5 + AssertThat 설정","categories":"spring java","author":"olkkani","emoji":"👻"},"fields":{"slug":"/java/start_gradle_project/junit5/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://olkkani.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"olkkani/olkkani.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/java/start_gradle_project/lombok/","nextSlug":"/java/path/","prevSlug":"/java/start_gradle_project/junit5/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}